{"tid":1503022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"826和你塞爆政府春袋！","createTime":"2019-08-24T19:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T16:54:46.000Z","uid":193663,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b9eaa18d3ee3b47bfc3c79d15e1743aed121df","tid":1503022,"uid":193663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:36:28.000Z","msg":"今時今日明顯剩係中聯辦同埋機場先會令政府緊張，搞咁多區分晒人力，個個分晒心，不如集中錫春袋！<br />\n<br />\n入機場三大好處<br />\n<br />\n1.機場最能夠影響香港經濟<br />\n2.機場入邊，警渣唔用得催淚彈或者槍，誤傷遊客，死都唔得掂<br />\n3.近身肉搏先最能夠將人數優勢發揮出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n警渣突然發出不反對通知書！居心叵測！<br />\n另外本人用呢個名極之少見，又咁啱有MTR職員指人冒認！司馬昭之心 路人皆知！<br />\n<br />\n香港人！<br />\nTHE HONG KONG WAY IS NOT ONLY A SLOGAN OR A GAME! IT IS THE TRUE AND ONLY HONG KONG WAY! <br />\n機場見！"},{"pid":"713ac309551197553d22ec7f54540a3df0b34fe1","tid":1503022,"uid":216405,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:37:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0194e83bc0600c022ee5732652fa586492f1bd88","tid":1503022,"uid":110509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:37:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月1 一定係機場<br />\n之後每個星期六/日 要有一日一定係機場</span></span>"},{"pid":"02e3daca81207bf4574a0eefad24db813a97dd60","tid":1503022,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1af487ee718eb13801dc20de7cf39c6b0c178ee","tid":1503022,"uid":236140,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:44:06.000Z","msg":"恕我直言，搞冧機場政府都唔會驚你！<br />\n<br />\n機場範圍有法庭命令，班狗有槍兼 full gear ! <br />\n<br />\n點解要同佢玩「正面」對抗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\"